title: Stellar Brew and Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Kitchen mixed with a coffee shop setting. Offers vegetarian food, raw food, as well as gluten free options; the non-veg items are turkey and fish. Veg items includes a veggie burger, tempeh sandwich, veggie wrap, salads with choice of add-ons, breakfast burrito and bowls. Also offers juices and smoothies.
